# Engineering decision blocks

Confirmed branch and expansion-gate choices must appear as **one durable report sentence per decision key** in the center panel. Copy is **node-owned**; runtime stores structured evidence, not prose.

**Source of truth:** `docs/rules.md` §12, §12b, §13. Contracts: `audits/contracts/nodes/paragraph.md`, `audits/contracts/nodes/parameter.md`. Center panel: `docs/desktopApp/center_panel_output_contract.md`.

## Copy ownership (single owner — no duplicates)

| Decision | Author on | PARAM keeps |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Straight pipe, pressure loading, similar paragraph gates | Paragraph `execution.interactions[]` (`question`, `help_text`, `options[].label`, `options[].help_text`, `options[].report_statement`) | `key`, `metadata.role`, `composer_input` binding only |
| Resolution branch (e.g. outside diameter method) | `PARAM-*` `resolution_branch_question`, `resolution_branch_help_text`, `resolution_branches[]` | Same node — not paragraph `execution.interactions` |

Resolve via `engine/messaging/decision_interaction_resolver.py`. **No** PARAM `user_prompt` / `composer_options` fallback for `NODE_OWNED_DECISION_KEYS`.

## Runtime vs presentation

| Layer | Owns |
| --- | --- |
| `Fact` + `ExecutionContext.Decision` | `decision_key`, `selected_value`, `selected_label`, `requesting_node_id`, `activated_node_ids` |
| `engineering_decision` transcript block | Authored `report_statement` after `{selected_label}`, `{requesting_reference}`, `{activated_reference}` substitution |

Record: `engine/state/decision_recorder.py`. Render: `engine/messaging/decision_statement.py`. Persist: `api/engineering_decision_transcript.py`.

## Center panel block

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| `display_role` | `engineering_decision` (**not** `scope_assumption`) |
| `block_id` | `engineering-decision-{decision_key}` |
| `source` | `engineering_decision` |
| Merge | Update in place on re-submit; no duplicate blocks on reload |

`ask_archive` / `answer_archive` stay audit-only — **do not** change `api/input_archive_transcript.py` for decisions.

## Composer (unresolved ask only)

- Prompt/options/help from resolver → `parameter_input_prompt` / `parameter_definitions`
- Checkbox: authored option labels (not hardcoded Yes/No)
- `PromptHelpIcon` when `option.help_text` or `branch.help_text` is set

## Do not

- Invent report sentences in planner, graph, API serializers, or frontend
- Use `scope_assumption` for branch decisions
- Emit unresolved prompts into `ordered_scroll_blocks`
- Add `if workflow ==` / `if node_id ==` branches in generic renderers

